   AKRON, Ohio -- American Business Computers Corp., which
makes products for the food-service industry, said it reached
an agreement that gives the Pepsi-Cola unit of PepsiCo Inc.,
Purchase, N.Y., exclusive rights to its soft-drink dispensers
and parts. Terms weren't disclosed.
   American Business Computers said the pact gives Pepsi
rights to new products and allows it to supply parts to other
dispenser makers.
