<HL>
   EC's Unemployment Rate
</HL>
<DATE>
07/10/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A13
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP
</CO>
<LP>
   LUXEMBOURG -- The seasonally adjusted unemployment rate in
the European Community for the first five months of this year
remained steady at 8.6%, the EC statistical office said.
   Unemployment ranged from 1.7% in Luxembourg to 16.6% in
Ireland, the report said.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   The latest unseasonally adjusted total of officially
registered jobless people in the EC was 13.9 million in
April.
