<LP>
   TEKELEC (Calabasas, Calif.) -- Daniel L. Brenner was
elected a director of this test equipment maker, filling a
longstanding vacancy. Mr. Brenner is a professor with the
Communications Law Program in the School of Law at the
University of California, Los Angeles.
</LP>
